manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Minlu 6ft 4-in-1 Nylon Braided Multi Charging Cable 3.5A The durability you’ve come to expect from Minlu 4 in 1 Charger Cord—now with universal compatibility. 6Ft/180cm and 4-IN-1 Nylon Braided Design ● 4Ft/120cm is perfect length for long distance charging, 4-in-1 retractable design, makes the cord portable and only need one cable when you are on a business trip or traveling. 4 IN 1 Retractable Multiple Charging Cables ● USB 2.0: Universally compatible for Phone, Micro-USB & Type-C devices, it has 4 different ports to USB cable for your most needs, it can charge 4 devices at the same time. ● iOS-Ports: With charging and data transmission functions. reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. I recently purchased the MINLU Multi Charging Cable, and it has exceeded my expectations. This 2-pack of 6ft cables with 4-in-1 functionality is a game-changer for anyone with multiple devices.The braided design adds a layer of durability that I've come to appreciate, ensuring that the cable can withstand the wear and tear of daily use. The 6ft length provides flexibility and convenience, allowing me to charge my devices even when the outlet is not right next to me.What truly sets this cable apart is its universal compatibility. With Dual iP, USB-C, and Micro USB connectors all in one, it's incredibly convenient. I can charge my iPhone, Android devices, and even my tablet with a single cable—no need to carry multiple cords anymore.The fast charging capability is another standout feature. I've noticed a significant decrease in charging time compared to other cables I've used in the past. This makes it especially handy when I'm in a rush and need a quick battery boost.Overall, the MINLU Multi Charging Cable is a reliable and versatile solution for all your charging needs. It simplifies my charging setup, reduces cable clutter, and ensures that I'm always prepared, no matter what device I'm using. I highly recommend it to anyone looking for a high-quality, all-in-one charging solution.
